            "body": "<p>Remove the 5 last lines of code, and you'll just have the DOM document in memory. Store this document in some field, rather than in a local variable.<\/p>\n\n<p>If that isn't sufficient, then please explain, with code, what you mean with <em>\"if I just try to access the document object below, it comes as empty\"<\/em>.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 12698702,
            "question_id": 12698561
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/e8cce88637f1a6e79155e8371e24b2e8?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
